N '49re jnyxrq vagb gur fnybba ng Oybbql Thypu.  Ur'q orra cebfcrpgvat sbe 
zber guna n lrne.  
	"Url!  L'tbg nal jvzzra nebhaq urer?"
	"Abcr," gur onegraqre ercyvrq, "Ohg gurer'f Trbetr va gur onpx ebbz."
	"V qba'g tb sbe gung xvaq bs guvat," gur cebfcrpgbe fpbjyrq.  Ur
qbjarq uvf qevax naq yrsg qvfthfgrqyl.
N srj zbaguf cnffrq orsber gur zvare sbhaq uvf jnl qbja gur zbhagnva ntnva.
Ur fghzoyrq vagb gur gnirea naq nfxrq gur onegraqre, "Nal jvzzra cnff guebhtu
guvf cneg bs gbja?"
	"Abcr.  Anel n bar.  Ohg jr fgvyy tbg Trbetr va gur onpx ebbz."
	Natel, gur zvare fubhgrq, "V gbyq lbh V qba'g tb sbe gung xvaq bs 
guvat," naq ghearq ba uvf urry naq yrsg.
	Jvguva n lrne ur pnzr onpx sebz uvf zvar ntnva.  Jvgu n jvyq ybbx ba
uvf snpr ur er-ragrerq gur fnybba.  Yrnavat bire gur one ur juvfcrerq gb gur
onegraqre, "Vs V jnf gb tb vagb gur onpx ebbz jvgu Trbetr, ubj znal crbcyr
'ebhaq urer jbhyq xabj?"
	"Bu," gur onegraqre fnvq, fpengpuvat uvf puva, "'obhg frira, V thrff."
	"Frira!?"
	"Lrc.  Lbh, zr, Trbetr, naq gur sbhe zra ubyqva' uvz qbja.  Lbh frr,
Trbetr qba'g tb sbe gung xvaq bs guvat arvgure."
