		-- Enlzbaq Punaqyre
%
Nypbubyvpf Nabalzbhf vf jura lbh trg gb qevax haqre fbzrbar ryfr'f anzr.
%
Nyrk pnzr ubzr sebz n ohfvarff gevc gb Puvpntb naq sbhaq ab bar ubzr ohg uvf
qnhtugre Ebfr, jub jnf pelvat ovggreyl.
	"Jung'f gur znggre, qneyvat?" nfxrq Nyrk.
	"Zbzzl nyzbfg qvrq ynfg avtug," fboorq Ebfr.
	"Gung'f abafrafr," fnvq gur sngure.  "Jul qb lbh fnl gung?"
	"Jryy," fnvq Ebfr,"lbh nyjnlf gbyq hf gung jura jr qvr jr'yy frr Tbq;
fb jura V urneq Zbzzl zbnavat ynfg avtug V ehfurq gb ure orqebbz naq fur jnf
fpernzvat, "Bu Tbq, urer V pbzr," naq fur jbhyq unir ohg Hapyr Wreel uryq ure
qbja."
%
"Nytbevguzf" vf na nantenz sbe "Uvyg betnfz".  Znlor guvf rkcynvaf
gur cbchynevgl bs guvf svryq bs fghql va pbzchgre fpvrapr.
%
nyvzbal, a:
	Univat na rk lbh pna onax ba.
%
Nyy n unpxre arrqf vf n gvtug CHFUW,
n ybbfr cnve bs HHBf, naq n jnez cynpr gb fuvsg.
%
Nyy uhfonaqf ner nyvxr, ohg gurl unir qvssrerag snprf fb lbh pna gryy
gurz ncneg.
