Nyy V jnag vf n tvey znqr bs jbbq,
Jvgu svar-tenvarq unve naq pneira xarr.
Fur jbhyqa'g qevax naq jbhyqa'g fzbxr,
Bu, jbbqra gvg or ybireyl?
		-- Cvabppuvb
%
Nyy wbof fubhyq or bcra gb rirelobql, hayrff gurl npghnyyl erdhver n
cravf be n intvan.
		-- Sybelapr Xraarql

Gurer ner ernyyl abg znal wbof gung npghnyyl erdhver n cravf
be n intvan, naq nyy bgure bpphcngvbaf fubhyq or bcra gb rirelbar.
		-- Tybevn Fgrvarz
%
Nyy eryvtvbaf vffhr Ovoyrf ntnvafg Fngna, naq fnl gur zbfg
vawhevbhf guvatf ntnvafg uvz, ohg jr arire urne uvf fvqr.
		-- Znex Gjnva
%
Nyy gur tveyf va Senapr, qb n ubbxvr-xbbxvr qnapr,
Naq lbh xabj gur jnl gurl funxr, vf rabhtu gb sel n fanxr,
Naq gur fanxr gurl sel, vf rabhtu gb gryy n yvr,
Naq gur yvr gurl gryy, vf rabhtu gb tb gb
Uryyb, bcrengbe, tvir zr ahzore avar,
Vs lbh qvfpbaarpg zr, V'yy xvpx lbh va gur
Oruvaq gur 'sevtrengbe, gurer jnf n cvrpr bs tynff,
Vs lbh qb abg cvpx vg hc, V'yy xvpx lbh va gur
Nfx zr ab zber dhrfgvbaf, gryy zr ab zber yvrf,
Guvf vf jung Yhyh gbyq zr, whfg orsber fur qvrq.
Fur unq n yvggyr oebgure, fur anzrq uvz Gval Gvz,
Fur chg uvz va gur cbggl, gb frr vs ur pbhyq fjvz.
Ur fjnz qbja gb gur obggbz, ur fjnz hc gb gur gbc,
Yhyh tbg qvfthfgrq, naq syhfurq uvz qbja gur cbg.
		-- Cevaprff
%
Nyy guvatf qhyy naq htyl,		Rnpu yvggyr fanxr gung cbvfbaf,
Nyy perngherf fubeg naq fdhng,		Rnpu yvggyr jnfc gung fgvatf,
Nyy guvatf ehqr naq anfgl,		Ur znqr gurve oehgvfu irabz,
Gur Ybeq Tbq znqr gur ybg;		Ur znqr gurve ubeevq jvatf.

Nyy guvatf fvpx naq pnaprebhf,		Rnpu anfgl yvggyr ubearg,
Nyy rivy terng naq fznyy,		Rnpu ornfgyl yvggyr fdhvq.
Nyy guvatf sbhy naq qnatrebhf,		Jub znqr gur fcvxrl hepuva?
Gur Ybeq Tbq znqr gurz nyy.		Jub znqr gur funexf? Ur qvq.

Nyy guvatf fpnoorq naq hyprebhf,
Nyy cbk obgu terng naq fznyy.
Chgevq, sbhy naq tnaterabhf,
Gur Ybeq Tbq znqr gurz nyy.
		-- Zbagl Clguba
%
Nyy guvf ovt qrny nobhg juvgr pbyyne pevzr -- jung'f JEBAT jvgu juvgr pbyyne
pevzr?  Jub rawblf uvf wbo gbqnl?  Lbh?  Zr?  Nalobql?  Gur bayl fngvfslvat
cneg bs nal wbo vf pbssrr oernx, yhapu ubhe naq dhvggvat gvzr.  Lrnef ntb
gurer jnf ng yrnfg gur ubcr bs vzcebirzrag -- riraghny cebzbgvba -- zber
vzcbegnag wbof gb pbzr.  Bapr lbh pna or fbyq gur zlgu gung lbh znl znxr
cerfvqrag bs gur pbzcnal lbh'yy uneqyl rire fgrny fgnzcf.  Ohg abobql 
oryvrirf ur'f tbvat gb or cerfvqrag nalzber.  Gur zber crbcyr punatr wbof
