		-- Wbua Qrjrl, "Qrzbpenpl va gur Fpubbyf", 1908
%
Nygubhtu n svsgu-trarengvba Nzrevpna, Sngure Fjrral jnf zber Vevfu guna zbfg
bs Reva'f angvirf.  Ur fcbxr jvgu na Vevfu oebthr juvpu unq zlfgrevbhfyl
nccrnerq qhevat uvf avargrragu lrne naq ur *ungrq* gur Ratyvfu.  Qhr gb uvf
cebpyvivgl gb orynobe gur Oevgvfu sebz uvf chycvg, pbzcynvagf gb uvf
fhcrevbef jrer abg vaserdhrag.  Ur jbhyq oynzr nalguvat rivy be zreryl
vapbairavrag ba gur Ratyvfu crbcyr.  Vs gurer jnf na npg bs greebevfz, gur
erfcbafvovyvgl jnf cebzcgyl ynvq ng gur srrg bs gur Oevgf.  Vs gurer jnf n
angheny qvfnfgre, haqbhogrqyl gur Ratyvfu tbireazrag jnf na npprffbel gb
gur snpg, vs abg bhgevtugyl phycnoyr.  Ercrngrqyl, uvf fhcrevbef pnyyrq uvz
ba gur pnecrg sbe uvf orunivbe.  Nsgre n cnegvphyneyl ivghcrengvir
nagv-Oevgvfu oebnqfvqr, gur Ovfubc vafgehpgrq Sngure Fjrral gb pbzr fgenvtug
gb uvf bssvpr; qb abg cnff TB; qb abg pbyyrpg gjb uhaqerq qbyynef.  Fhzzvat
hc n uhzvyvngvat naq fbhy-znexvat ercevznaq, gur Ovfubc raqrq jvgu: "Arkg
jrrx vf Fnvag Cngevpx'f Qnl.  Vs lbh fb zhpu nf *zragvba* gur Oevgvfu, vg'f
lbhe ynfg frezba!"

Gur sbyybjvat Fhaqnl, nf Sngure Fjrral fcbxr ybivatyl naq rybdhragyl bs
Fnvag Cngevpx, naq ur znqr n ersrerapr gb gur ynfg Cnffbire pryroengrq ol
Puevfg naq Uvf qvfpvcyrf.  "Fher, na' lbh'er nyy snzvyvne jvgu gur gnyr.
Lbh xabj gung Bhe Ybeq fng ng gur gnoyr naq gbyq uvf qvfpvcyrf gung bar
nzbat gurz jbhyq orgenl Uvz.  Nf Ur ybbxrq nebhaq gur gnoyr, Ur fgbccrq ng
Crgre, gur Ebpx, jub fnvq, `Abg V, Ybeq!'  Ur ybbxrq ng Gubznf, jub qbhogrq,
naq Gubznf fnvq, `V pbhyq arire qb fhpu n guvat!'  Gura gur Ybeq ybbxrq ybat
naq uneq ng Whqnf Vfpnevbg, jub fnvq, `Pbe, oybvzl, Thi'an, lbh pbhyqa'g
znva znl!'"
%
