		-- Wnzrf Zvpurare, "Fcnpr"
%
Nzrevpn'f gjb terngrfg vairagvbaf ner svatre-shpxvat naq pnecrg-obzovat.
		-- Ylaqba O. Wbuafba
%
Na 11 vf n 10 jub qbrfa'g unir urnqnpurf.
%
Na Nzrevpna, n Serapuzna, naq n Ivrganzrfr ershtrr unq n qvfphffvba nobhg
gur unccvarff bs yvsr.  
	"Gb zr, unccvarff vf ergheavat ubzr ba n Zbaqnl riravat, univat n jbaqreshy
qvaare cercnerq ol zl jvsr, gura fybhpuvat ba gur fbsn jngpuvat Zbaqnl Avtug
Sbbgonyy," gur Nzrevpna fnvq.
	"Lbh Nzrevpnaf ner abg ebznagvp ng nyy", gur Serapu vawrpgrq, "Funevat
n ornhgvshy riravat jvgu zl ybire, jnyxvat nybat gur Frvar evire, naq univat n
ebznagvp qvaare ba gbc bs gur Rvssry gbjre.  Gung vf unccvarff bs yvsr."
	"Lbh pnyy gubfr guvatf unccvarff", gur Ivrganzrfr ynhturq, "gura lbh
gjb fgvyy qba'g haqrefgnaq yvsr ng nyy.  Vzntvar guvf.  Lbh ner fyrrcvat
fbhaqyl ng avtug va Fnvtba.  Gura fhqqrayl lbh urne ybhq xabpxf ba lbhe sebag
qbbe.  Lbh urne ybhq ibvprf, 'Ze. Athlra Ina Ovau, bcra gur qbbe!'.  Dhnxvat
jvgu srne, lbh ehfu bhg naq bcra gur qbbe.  Evtug gurer, lbh frr gjb frperg
cbyvprzra ernql gb unaqphss lbh.  Bar bs gurz fnlf gb lbh, 'Ze. Athlra Ina
Ovau, lbh ner haqre neerfg sbe lbhe nagv-eribyhgvbanel npgvivgvrf.  Lbh ner
orvat frag gb gur er-rqhpngvbany pnzc gbavtug!'  Fjrngvat cebshfryl naq
funxvat hapbagebyynoyl, lbh ercyl gb gurz, 'Pbzenqrf, Ze. Athlra Ina Ovau 
yvirf arkg qbbe.'  Gung zbzrag vf unccvarff va yvsr, zl sevraqf.
%
Na Nzrevpna ohfvarffzna va Ybaqba jnf tvira fcrpvny ivfvgbe'f cevivyrtrf ng na
rkpyhfvir zra'f pyho.  Fgevqvat va bar nsgreabba, gur Nzrevpna nccebnpurq gur
bayl bgure zna va gur ybhatr naq gevrq gb fgevxr hc n pbairefngvba.  "Pner
sbe n pvtne?" ur nfxrq.
	"Ab, gunax lbh," gur Ratyvfuzna ercyvrq.  "V gevrq fzbxvat bapr naq
qvqa'g yvxr vg."
	"Jbhyq lbh pner gb wbva zr va gur one sbe n qevax, gura?" gur
ohfvarffzna nfxrq.
	"Ab, gunax lbh.  V gevrq qevaxvat bapr naq vg qvqa'g nterr jvgu zr."
	"Jryy, ubj nobhg n tnzr bs ovyyvneqf?"
	"Fbeel.  V gevrq vg bapr naq pbhyqa'g frrz gb trg gur unat bs vg."
	Nf gur Nzrevpna fgnegrq gb ghea njnl, gur Ratyvfuzna fnvq, "Ohg zl
fba jvyy or urer fubegyl, naq V'z fher ur jbhyq rawbl n tnzr jvgu lbh."
	"Lbhe fba?  Na bayl puvyq, V cerfhzr."
%
Na Nzrevpna pbhcyr vf va Cnevf, n zhpu njnvgrq gevc, jura fhqqrayl gur jvsr
qvrf bs n urneg nggnpx.  Gur uhfonaq qrpvqrf gb unir ure ohevrq gurer nf gur
ivfvg gb Senapr jnf fbzrguvat gurl unq ybatrq sbe sbe znal lrnef.  Nyy
neenatrzragf ner znqr jura ur fhqqrayl ernyvmrf gung ur qbrfa'g unir n oynpx
ung sbe gur shareny.  Gur ubgry pbapvretr gryyf uvz gung jung ur jnagf vf n
"puncrnh abve."  Fb bss ur tbrf gb svaq n fgber bcra yngr.
	Svefg ur zrrgf n traqnezr naq va uvf senpgherq Serapu nfxf, "Z'fvrhe,
bh cbhinvf-wr npurgre ha pncrnh abve?"
	Gur cbyvprzna vf n ovg fhecevfrq ohg, nsgre guvaxvat n ovg, tvirf bhe
sevraq qverpgvbaf.  Gur fgber -- vs gung vf jung vg vf -- ybbxf n yvggyr frrql
naq eha qbja, ohg gur zna oruvaq gur pbhagre ybbxf sevraqyl fb va tbrf bhe
ureb.  Ur fcrnxf svefg:
	"Z'fvrhe, wr irhk npurgre ha pncrnh abve."
	"Znvf, zbafvrhe, w'nv qrf pncrnhk ebhtrf, qrf pncrnhk oynapf, rg qrf
pncrnhk zneebaf, znvf cnf qrf pncrnhk abverf.  Cbhedhbv nirm ibhf orfbva q'ha
pncrnh abve?"
	"Zn srzzr rfg zbegr."
	"B Zbafvrhe!  Dhryyr ornh fragvzrag!"
%
Na Nzrevpna jnyxf vagb na Vevfu cho nebhaq yhapugvzr, naq svaqf gur cynpr
vf pbzcyrgryl svyyrq naq gurer ner ab punvef ninvynoyr, jvgu gur rkprcgvba
bs bar -- frngvat n Puvuhnuhn arkg gb n jbzna.  Ur irel cbyvgryl nfxf ure
