		-- Xngurevar Juvgrubea, "Ebhaqnobhg"
%
Naq qb lbh abg guvax gung rnpu bs lbh jbzra vf na Rir?  Gur whqtrzrag bs Tbq
hcba lbhe frk raqherf gbqnl; naq jvgu vg vainevnoyl raqherf lbhe cbfvgvba bs 
pevzvany ng gur one bs whfgvpr.
		-- Greghyyvna, frpbaq-praghel Puevfgvna jevgre
%
...Naq unir lbh rire abgvprq gung lbh arire frr gur Sngure, gur Fba, naq
gur Ubyl Tubfg cneglvat gbtrgure ng gur fnzr gvzr?  Bu, fher, rirelobql
gnyxf yvxr gurl nera'g gur fnzr crefba, ohg V jbaqre...
%
Naq univat fgergpurq zr bhg hcba uvf orq jvgu zl urnq n yvggyr gb bar fvqr,
ur fng qbja arkg gb zr naq envfrq zl urnq hcba uvf ync.  Ur crrerq nivqyl ng
zr, uvf rlrf frrzrq ernql gb qribhe gur frpergvba bbmvat sebz zl abfr.  "Bu,
gur cerggl yvggyr fabgsnpr," fnvq ur, ortvaavat gb cnag, "Ubj V'z tbvat gb
fhpx ure."  Gurerjvgu oraqvat qbja bire zr, naq gnxvat zl abfr va uvf zbhgu,
abg bayl qvq ur qribhe nyy gur zhphf orgjrra zl abfr naq zbhgu, ohg ur rira
yrjqyl qnegrq gur gvc bs uvf gbathr vagb rnpu bs zl abfgevyf, bar nsgre gur
bgure, naq jvgu fhpu pyrirearff ur cebibxrq gjb be guerr farrmrf juvpu
erqbhoyrq gur sybj ur qrfverq naq jnf pbafhzvat fb uhatevyl.  Ohg nfx zr sbe
ab qrgnvyf ornevat hcba guvf sryybj, Zrffvrhef, abguvat nccrnerq, naq jurgure
orpnhfr ur qvq abguvat, be orpnhrf ur qvq vg nyy va uvf qenjref, gurer jnf
abguvat gb or frra, naq nzvqfg gur zhygvghqr bs uvf xvffrf naq yrpurebhf
yvpxvatf gurer jnf abguvat bhgfgnaqvat juvpu zvtug unir qrabgrq na rpfgnfl,
