Jryy, guvf jnf n chmmyre, pbaprqrq gur qbpgbe, jub cebprrqrq gb ersre gb gur
rabezbhf ersrerapr gbzrf oruvaq uvf qrfx, zhggrevat gb uvzfrys.
	"Ybbxf tbbq, srryf tbbq...  Ab, lbh ybbx yvxr uryy.  Ybbxf tbbq,
srryf greevoyr...  Anu, lbh srry svar, evtug?"
Guhzovat shevbhfyl guebhtu nabgure ibyhzr, ur fnvq,
	"Ybbxf greevoyr, srryf greevoyr...  Abcr, gung jba'g qb vg rvgure."
Svanyyl, "Ybbxf greevoyr, srryf greevsvp... Nun!!  Lbh'er n intvan!"
%
Unir lbh rire ernyyl gubhtug nobhg gurer orvat n fvzcyr fbyhgvba gb
Nzrevpn'f ceboyrzf?  Jul, jr pbhyq fbyir nyy bs bhe enj zngrevnyf
qvssvphygvrf, sbervta pbzcyvpngvbaf rgp. bire n ybat jrrxraq.  Vs jr
