Sbeghar -- C.B. Obk 478
%
Frrzf yvxr gurer jrer gurfr gjb qbtf va n irg'f jnvgvat ebbz, rnpu rlrvat
gur bgure fhfcvpvbhfyl.  Bar bs gurz gheaf gb gur bgure.
	"Jung ner lbh urer sbe?" ur nfxf.
	"Jryy," ercyvrf gur bgure, "V jnf srryvat ernyyl onq gur bgure qnl,
naq Znfgre'f fvk lrne byq fba fgnegrq obgurevat zr. V gevrq gb vtaber vg,
ohg V jnf srryvat fb ebggra gung V ovg uvf unaq."
	"Lrnu, V abj jung lbh zrna.  Fb, jung ner lbh urer sbe?"
	"Rez ... jryy ... Znfgre erpxbaf gung V'z gbb ivpvbhf, fb V'z tbvat
gb or ... lbh xabj ... V'z tbvat gb unir gur *bcrengvba*."
	"Bu.  Jryy, V'z fbeel," flzcnguvfrq gur svefg qbt.
	Gvzr cnffrq. Gur nobhg-gb-or-arhgrerq qbt pbhturq cbyvgryl.
	"Fb," ur nfxrq, "Jung ner lbh va urer sbe?"
	"Bu, abguvat ernyyl," gur bgure ercyvrq, rzoneenffrq.
