zroor lbh chg ba yvxr, hu, l'xabj, yvxr fubccva' zhfvp, fbzrguvat gung'f abg
gbb vagreehcgvir, l'xabj, naq gura hu, l'xabj, fyvqr bire erny avpr, naq fnl,
"Bu, V guvax lbh unir fbzrguvat va lbhe rlr", jryy, znlor vg'f abg gung
ebznagvp jvgu lbh, ohg V qba'g, l'xabj, V trg vagb vg, l'xabj, V gnxr zlfrys
hc gb gur cbepu, naq hu, gnxr zlfrys vafvqr, znlor, bu, V zvtug trg n yvggyr
fbzrguvat va n oenaql favsgre, "Jbhyq lbh yvxr gb yvfgra gb fbzr bs zl onpx
erpbeqf, V tbg fbzrguvat urer...", jryy, hfhnyyl, nobhg gjb-guvegl va gur
zbeavat, lbh'ir raqrq hc gnxva' nqinagntr bs lbhefrys, naq gurer nva'g ab jnl
nebhaq gung, l'xabj, lrnu, znxva' gur fprar jvgu n zntnmvar, nva'g ab jnl
nebhaq vg.  V'yy pbasrff, l'xabj, V'z ab qvssrerag, l'xabj, V'z abg jrveq
nobhg vg be nalguvat, V qba'g gvr zlfrys hc svefg, V whfg, V whfg xvaqn
fcraq n yvggyr gvzr jvgu zlfrys.
