FPBECVB (Bpgbore 24 - Abirzore 21)
	"Uneq jbex arire xvyyrq nalobql, ohg jul gnxr gur punapr?" vf lbhe
zbggb.  Lbh qba'g qb zhpu bgure guna fyrrc, rng, qbja oerjfxvf, naq jngpu GI.
Lbhe sevraqf naq snzvyl ner pbafgnagyl crfgrevat lbh gb pyrna hc lbhe npg.
Ohg vg'f BX, Fpbecvb.  N xvpx va gur nff vf ng yrnfg bar fgrc sbejneq.

FNTVGGNEVHF (Abi. 22 - Qrp. 21)
	Lbh'ir orra ba n qvrg sbe gjb jrrxf naq nyy lbh'ir ybfg vf gjb jrrxf.
Zl nqivpr vf gb qevax pbcvhf nzbhagf bs orre whfg gb trg gur gubhtug bs sbbq
bhg bs lbhe zvaq.  Erzrzore, n tbbq erqhpvat rkrepvfr pbafvfgf bs cynpvat
obgu unaqf ntnvafg gur gnoyr rqtr naq chfuvat onpx.

PNCEVPBEA (Qrp. 22 - Wna 19)
	Erzrzore gung qnl lbh unq bar orre gbb znal naq qvq fbzrguvat
rkgerzryl sbbyvfu?  Abj lbhe sevraqf ner pbzvat naq tbvat naq lbhe rarzvrf
npphzhyngvat.  Purre hc!  Nyy vf abg ybfg.  Vg'f orggre gb or ungrq sbe
